    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you say 'sophisticated and understated' hairstyles for women, could you be a bit more specific? Like, are there certain textures or styles that look more 'executive' than others? I want to make sure my clients aren't accidentally looking too casual or even unprofessional because of how they wear their hair.",
